name: neckbreakers
description:
neckbreakers is the first song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. neckbreakers was one of those beats that just made itself. Once I had the drums, everything else fell into place smoothly. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "neckbreaking souls" I was blown away but was generated and knew I had to use it for the art. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality WAV files!
